{"type": "article", "id": 23035, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-01T07:30:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 24124, "name": "Smarin"}, {"id": 24153, "name": "agape"}, {"id": 24154, "name": "SturlesiDesign"}, {"id": 24155, "name": "Ponti"}, {"id": 24156, "name": "Siegenthaler & Co"}, {"id": 954, "name": "Herman Miller"}, {"id": 24157, "name": "charles wilson"}, {"id": 22532, "name": "Patricia Urquiola"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 56, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702104514VTFlyKzcoZurXmCG.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p>\n<h2>Les Angles by smarin</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/23000.html\">昨天介绍了法国品牌 smarin 的沙发 dune</a>，他们最新推出的也是像小山一样的沙发组。它有 8 个几何组件，都是用羊毛制成的，其中 4 种是方形的底座，任意放上三角形或梯形的靠背。不用的时候，靠墙排成连绵起伏的小山丘，可以随意拿走一块作为靠垫，是放在商务空间里的很好的装饰。售价 216 欧元起，<a href=\"http://shop.smarin.net/en/61-shapes\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061543477QUJsSqg10oFlwmN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154347uI7QX8hUcJK1AyFG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154348b0ldKzhEt3LT17Sr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154348BH6Ndwvux1oTRX2r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154349Jz3QHn61Fd2iWBom.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>carafe by herman miller &amp; charles wilson</h2>\n<p>这是一张兼具收纳和用餐功能的餐桌 carafe，用橡木制作。简洁优雅的外形让它具有餐桌的特征，桌子下面有简易的储藏空间和接线孔，让手机和电脑的电源线有了好去处。实现工作和生活的转化，是适合现代人的桌子。它有三种尺寸，<a href=\"http://charleswilsondesign.com\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061543490RCYOcqJ7wH8agAV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91809291\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154350LNoR7n0Bfb5pVHWU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82151589\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154350xLkGUDnrjTKHdS1m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18581907\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154351vmhKliNGb2WVUfLt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32151589\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154351tTfzHmcWC7Fk3i98.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31662592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>cuna &amp; larian &amp; vieques by agape &amp; Patricia Urquiola </h2>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>这是西班牙女设计师 Patricia Urquiola 为意大利品牌 agape 推出的一系列浴缸，造型传统而极简。cuna 是由不锈钢管框架支撑了水盆，很轻盈。而 larian 则显得方正典雅许多，边缘略有向内倾斜，是一种开放的姿态，水缸之外的细长的水龙头成为具有对比性的装饰，有些是黑白相对的。而他们从前合作的 vieques 是由钢铁制作的，另带有柚木书架与靠背放在浴缸的边缘，很有趣。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061543524YcnUu5RST1j7HqO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93398533\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154352NKE51lmRy2eUDc9P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154353lHawtBMcZexT1WPN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78850856\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154353LICxuVvDgER2JPO3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66136919\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154353eRwC5GMcdOqtzoUN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71638142\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>aka Edison bulbs by Sturlesi Design</h2>\n<p>这组灯看似像旧时的钨丝灯泡，但它十足是 LED 灯。在水泥灯头下连接了扁平的玻璃模块，上面用激光雕刻了灯丝线，顺着灯光恰好可以看到清晰的纹路，有种特别的工业感，适合家居或酒吧环境。设计者来自以色列，6 种不同的玻璃模块可相互替换，<a href=\"http://www.illuminite.me\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154354xGETrCdo8meYBtPj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16361679\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154354fk79TWmBLsz2c8Vl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154355vZIyc3dBUAwD2Nko.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154355UVCQ52SATjGDthrJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061543567Px3npjzoDHAEk6t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Dune by Ponti </h2>\n<p>这套铝制的刀叉餐具名为 dune（沙丘），它的手柄和叉勺是垂直关系，使得过度地段形成一条曲线，就像一个小的沙丘，很有质感。这种设计挑战了人们的惯有用法，但设计师解释这是一种实验风格，它更像手术室的临床工具，象征着烹饪时的无限可能。搭配铝的材质，使这套餐具拥有轻盈的特征和质感。<a href=\"http://www.andreaponti.com/projects/dune.html\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154356ePbJuKSy5GXHF3qk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061543571wicCReHlGVF9fsk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061543578h4vDHcM5OpqPiKN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154357ga6hZwYtCJA7FcEP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154358t7XdpIMgvOsjqFel.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86935639\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>BLEND by Siegenthaler &amp; Co</h2>\n<p>丰富绚丽的色彩已成为果蔬汁的卖点，这款哥伦比亚的果蔬汁也有漂亮的渐变色。Siegenthaler &amp; Co 使用了日出日落时的天空的色彩来表现自然无添加等传统的概念，在包装纸的下面，颜色渐变到果蔬汁本来的色彩。原有的混合果汁有几款都是相近的黄色，但在包装纸上使用了蓝或绿等不同的颜色，从而使 5 种果汁之间构成了很强的区别度。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154358tVW6ND8IgnsT5SG3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154359LivK6MjCUd28YehG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061543595XzCfMZJqHNVLWlQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154359Y5BQOEFyNu3fhKS0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154400INyjeqtLXo0QWzT6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n\n"}